00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:12,530
♪Longing during the day
and loneliness at night♪

2
00:00:12,830 --> 00:00:19,700
♪Clouds drift and curl,
and the cold rain falls again♪

3
00:00:20,460 --> 00:00:26,100
♪Green grass once dreamed of the world
and enlightened me♪

4
00:00:26,420 --> 00:00:32,990
♪I crossed the sea of suffering
but couldn't escape your gaze♪

5
00:00:33,190 --> 00:00:39,930
♪Look at the bright moon
across the Milky Way♪

6
00:00:40,060 --> 00:00:46,990
♪All love poems will record our story
from now on♪

7
00:00:47,060 --> 00:00:53,700
♪The thought of the distant mountain
makes my heart ache for my hometown♪

8
00:00:53,840 --> 00:01:01,520
♪Stone of Three Lifetimes reflects fate.
You once rode past on horseback♪

9
00:01:02,020 --> 00:01:03,720
=Just Wanna Be With You=

10
00:01:03,720 --> 00:01:05,360
(Adapted From
Zhihu Novelist, Little Qi's)

11
00:01:05,360 --> 00:01:07,260
("Three Marriages
to the Underworld Lord")

12
00:01:07,260 --> 00:01:10,260
=Episode 22=

13
00:01:44,599 --> 00:01:45,760
(Jiang Zhiyu.)

14
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:49,159
(You and Jiang Jinghuai
are bound by fate.)

15
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:53,439
(Only by severing love
can you save the world.)

16
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:54,719
I don't believe in fate!

17
00:02:02,439 --> 00:02:03,519
(Jiang Zhiyu.)

18
00:02:04,519 --> 00:02:05,840
(Forget him.)

19
00:02:06,159 --> 00:02:09,800
I will never forget him.

20
00:02:11,599 --> 00:02:12,199
(Yu.)

21
00:02:13,960 --> 00:02:15,199
(You shouldn't be doing this.)

22
00:02:16,599 --> 00:02:17,280
(Yu!)

23
00:02:21,039 --> 00:02:21,800
Huai.

24
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,439
Is that you, Huai?

25
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:29,199
Huai.

26
00:02:30,039 --> 00:02:31,479
What's the point

27
00:02:31,759 --> 00:02:33,719
of living without you?

28
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:36,599
I will save you, no matter what.

29
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:38,280
(Leave this place at once.)

30
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,120
(Go!)

31
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:41,120
No.

32
00:02:41,159 --> 00:02:42,319
(Go!)

33
00:02:43,719 --> 00:02:44,439
Huai.

34
00:02:45,599 --> 00:02:46,360
Huai!

35
00:02:47,039 --> 00:02:48,000
Huai!

36
00:02:52,639 --> 00:02:54,319
True love is nothing but sincere.

37
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:56,240
The heart leads the way.

38
00:02:56,719 --> 00:02:58,240
Let it be known for eternity that

39
00:02:58,439 --> 00:03:00,759
fate has brought us together again!

40
00:03:01,639 --> 00:03:03,000
I don't believe in fate!

41
00:03:03,159 --> 00:03:04,879
I don't believe in fate!

42
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:10,800
Huai.

43
00:03:12,334 --> 00:03:14,150
♪And I get soaked alone♪

44
00:03:14,159 --> 00:03:15,120
Huai.

45
00:03:16,094 --> 00:03:17,934
♪Where they belong♪

46
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:20,759
I will find you.

47
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:32,203
♪I search for you across the vast sky,
but where are you now?♪

48
00:03:32,599 --> 00:03:33,879
Huai.

49
00:03:35,870 --> 00:03:37,338
♪The clouds' traces♪

50
00:03:39,599 --> 00:03:40,479
Huai.

51
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:43,199
Huai!

52
00:03:45,310 --> 00:03:47,461
Where are you, Huai?

53
00:03:47,461 --> 00:03:52,850
♪It can only rest inside your dreams♪

54
00:03:54,759 --> 00:03:55,800
I will...

55
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:59,719
I will get you out of here.

56
00:04:00,160 --> 00:04:07,310
♪If I were granted
a pair of splendid wings♪

57
00:04:07,370 --> 00:04:12,380
♪I could chase memories
in place of the right to love♪

58
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:15,030
♪But the Milky Way never ends♪

59
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:21,830
♪In this thin robe,
I wait for your reply♪

60
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:58,279
Lass.

61
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:01,600
You just recovered from your injury
on the Bridge of Severance.

62
00:05:01,880 --> 00:05:02,800
It's storming out here.

63
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:05,080
Come inside and take your medicine.

64
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:08,079
He's not coming back.

65
00:05:10,199 --> 00:05:10,879
Right?

66
00:05:25,639 --> 00:05:26,639
Just live well.

67
00:05:35,330 --> 00:05:39,018
♪When the fog thickens
and the sky turns desolate♪

68
00:05:39,207 --> 00:05:44,072
♪Even wild grass
draws my gaze to you♪

69
00:05:45,490 --> 00:05:49,229
♪Right now I can't hide
the joy in my heart♪

70
00:05:49,340 --> 00:05:53,789
♪It spreads through the swirling mist♪

71
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:55,800
Yu.

72
00:05:55,927 --> 00:05:59,629
♪You'll never know,
I've never longed for anyone so♪

73
00:05:59,709 --> 00:06:04,341
♪I've braved countless thorns
for just one glance♪

74
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:05,960
It's a downpour.

75
00:06:05,960 --> 00:06:07,680
Why are you still standing there?
Come on in.

76
00:06:10,399 --> 00:06:10,959
Come on in.

77
00:06:11,927 --> 00:06:15,861
♪I couldn't help
but take one step closer to you♪

78
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:19,060
♪I'm the fog born in the forest♪

79
00:06:19,140 --> 00:06:21,700
♪You're the wind that rises at dusk♪

80
00:06:21,700 --> 00:06:26,790
♪You have traveled a thousand miles.
Deep love and everything♪

81
00:06:26,830 --> 00:06:29,490
♪Even if it's just a moment's pause♪

82
00:06:29,490 --> 00:06:36,550
♪How could I be content
with just one look at you?♪

83
00:06:37,210 --> 00:06:39,810
♪I'm the fog born in the forest♪

84
00:06:39,810 --> 00:06:42,260
♪You're the wind that rises at dusk♪

85
00:06:42,260 --> 00:06:43,781
♪Wherever you go♪

86
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,439
Who are you?

87
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:48,839
Why don't you say something?

88
00:06:50,839 --> 00:06:51,360
I...

89
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:53,120
I'm one of the foxfolk.
My name is Jiu.

90
00:07:02,079 --> 00:07:02,920
I like you.

91
00:07:04,519 --> 00:07:05,639
(That day, you said)

92
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,160
(you liked me.)

93
00:07:08,399 --> 00:07:09,600
(I didn't give you an answer.)

94
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:11,680
(Because)

95
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:15,120
(I gave you that poem,
which goes like this:)

96
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:19,279
(If you are as sincere as me,)

97
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:23,439
(then I won't let our love be in vain.)

98
00:07:24,639 --> 00:07:25,399
(At that moment,)

99
00:07:26,199 --> 00:07:27,600
(I had already fallen for you.)

100
00:07:29,879 --> 00:07:32,240
(I still remember our vow.)

101
00:07:33,879 --> 00:07:36,279
(And I want our love to be eternal.)

102
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:37,920
(You must do this bow)

103
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:40,600
(with me.)

104
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:44,959
(I, Jiang Jinghuai, swear)

105
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:46,800
(by the snow.)

106
00:07:47,839 --> 00:07:48,879
(In every lifetime,)

107
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:51,319
(I will love only Jiang Zhiyu.)

108
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:53,399
We've come a long way together.

109
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:55,319
It really hasn't been easy.

110
00:07:57,399 --> 00:07:58,240
Jiang Jinghuai.

111
00:07:59,270 --> 00:07:59,781
I love you.

112
00:07:59,803 --> 00:08:02,247
♪I'm the fog born in the forest♪

113
00:08:02,290 --> 00:08:04,850
♪You're the wind that rises at dusk♪

114
00:08:04,930 --> 00:08:09,774
♪Wherever you go,
my heart quietly follows♪

115
00:08:10,199 --> 00:08:10,839
Jiang Zhiyu.

116
00:08:16,319 --> 00:08:17,079
I love you too.

117
00:08:20,350 --> 00:08:22,989
♪I'm the fog born in the forest♪

118
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:25,374
♪You're the wind that rises at dusk♪

119
00:08:27,279 --> 00:08:27,839
(Yu.)

120
00:08:29,439 --> 00:08:30,959
(I just want you to live well.)

121
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:32,799
No!

122
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:36,600
No wonder I couldn't
hear your heartbeat that day.

123
00:08:36,639 --> 00:08:39,639
Why couldn't I hear your heartbeat?

124
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:41,159
When I fell for you,

125
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:42,679
my heart

126
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,039
had already left with you.

127
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,279
You lied to me.

128
00:08:46,399 --> 00:08:48,039
You lied to me!

129
00:08:51,352 --> 00:08:54,170
♪I'll follow you to the ends
of the mountains and forests♪

130
00:08:54,170 --> 00:09:00,341
♪A life adrift at last
finds a place to belong♪

131
00:09:23,559 --> 00:09:24,080
(Yu.)

132
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:27,279
(Yu.)

133
00:10:11,270 --> 00:10:17,090
♪Dark clouds cover the stars
without a trace of light♪

134
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:23,080
♪Waiting for the wind
to clear the grey away♪

135
00:10:25,340 --> 00:10:28,910
♪Sudden rain falls
and I get soaked alone♪

136
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:32,710
♪Even larks know where they belong♪

137
00:10:33,050 --> 00:10:38,530
♪It is not about running away♪

138
00:10:40,370 --> 00:10:46,730
♪I search for you across the vast sky,
but where are you now?♪

139
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:52,680
♪I become a wisp of wind,
wiping away the clouds' traces♪

140
00:10:54,530 --> 00:10:57,970
♪I long to disappear without a trace,
wrapped in mystery♪

141
00:10:58,080 --> 00:11:01,750
♪If I send your loneliness
back to the sky♪

142
00:11:02,140 --> 00:11:07,500
♪It can only rest inside your dreams♪

143
00:11:07,620 --> 00:11:12,600
♪You and I gaze
at the endless Milky Way♪

144
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:14,730
♪Holding each other so near♪

145
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:22,110
♪If I were granted
a pair of splendid wings♪

146
00:11:22,170 --> 00:11:27,180
♪I could chase memories
in place of the right to love♪

147
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:29,830
♪But the Milky Way never ends♪

148
00:11:29,920 --> 00:11:36,630
♪In this thin robe,
I wait for your reply♪
